AUDIO: 'Your AI agent is blind your code base and it brings dependencies you didn\'t even know existed. And GitNexus just gave us this insane vision. The real problem here is AI usually sees one file at a time. It misses imports, call chains, inheritance, and even execution'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'flows. So we refactor, deploy, go to sleep, and we just wake up with all these new problems. Because your code base is a graph and AI is still guessing blind. GitNexus turns your entire repo into a real knowledge graph. Every'

[00:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'symbol, every dependency, every call chain, every flow. It uses tree-sitter parsing so it stays accurate instead of hallucinating. You can trace execution paths, spot clusters, and finally see'

[00:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'how the code actually connects. And the best part is it runs fully local. It\'s private, it\'s fast, it\'s yours. That means we can ask real questions when we use this. Like, what happens if I change this code? Is it going to break? Is this'

